# Angular Material Theming Patterns

## Custom Theme Architecture
- **Brand Integration**: Custom color palettes generated following Material guidelines
- **Multi-Mode Support**: Light and dark theme support with proper switching
- **Accessibility**: Color contrast ratios meeting WCAG 2.1 AA requirements

## Component Theme Consistency
- **Centralized Theming**: Component theming centralized and consistently applied
- **Theme Mixins**: Component-specific theme mixins properly implemented
- **Color Usage**: Consistent theme color usage across all components

## Multi-Tenant Theming
- **Runtime Switching**: Theme system supports tenant-specific customization with runtime switching
- **Asset Management**: Tenant branding assets properly managed with fallbacks
- **Configuration**: Tenant themes configurable without code changes

## Typography System
- **Material Integration**: Custom fonts properly integrated with Material typography system
- **Financial Data**: Typography optimized for financial data display and readability
- **Responsive**: Typography responsive across different screen sizes

## Verification Commands
- **Theme Files**: `find src/theme -name "*.scss" | head -5`
- **Material Usage**: `grep -rn "@angular/material" src/app/`
- **Theme Variables**: `grep -rn "mat-palette" src/theme/`

## File References
- **Theme Configuration**: `src/theme/` directory with SCSS theme files
- **Material Modules**: Material module imports and configuration
- **Component Theming**: Component-specific theme implementations
- **Brand Assets**: Tenant-specific logo and asset management patterns
